                     <interp inst="t18201206-182-person1677" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. At half-past nine o'clock I was called in, and took charge of the prisoner; she said, no watchman should take her. The bedstated was stripped; I took her to the watch-house.</p>

